# {{ .ProjectName }}

Project scaffold generated by `ialang init`.

## Run

    go run ./cmd/ialang run main.ia

## Config

Configuration file is located at `config/app.json`:

- `app.name`: greeting target shown by `main.ia`
- `log.level`: `debug|info|warn|error`
- `log.json`: output JSON logs when `true`
- `log.outputPath`: log file path, empty means stdout

## Build Package

    ialang build main.ia -o app.iapkg
    ialang run-pkg app.iapkg
    ialang build-bin main.ia -o {{ .ProjectName }}.exe

